{
  "stem": "1479.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In fact, the number on the list-- numbers seven and eight-- are the numbers of my sister and myself.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And after the Schindler's list, what was going on, I could not tell you how the list, who made the list.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The fact was, when the day came, we were loaded into cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we heard rumors only that the 300-- the selected 300 women, Schindler's women-- we will bypass Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we will be traveling directly to his newly established factory in Czechoslovakia in Brunnlitz.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "However, things turned out differently.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Once we were in the cattle cars, we arrived in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I found-- we-- my sister and I-- we found out maybe a day or two later, because when they selected a group of men to clean the ghetto, and they were loading people on the open trucks, whatever, bringing them from the ghetto to Plaszow, burying them-- to be buried in the mass graves, one of the men who worked over there, he came up and he told us that he saw the bodies of my both parents.",
      "word_count": 78
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I cannot be completely sure.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But there were times we were over 20,000 people in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the numbers usually varied.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was many times much more.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The number was greater.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And sometime was lower.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It depend how many people were deported.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were brought by force.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Plaszow, they brought people from Hungary.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They brought people from other southern European countries.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember the Hungarian people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they were brought from Greece, from somewhere else, to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm talking about Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's what we heard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "However, things worked out differently because we were brought to Auschwitz in the cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Auschwitz is the most--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were packed in the cars.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
